@@TJvAVICapture.OnFrame
Summary
  The event triggered when a frame is ready, in a non streaming capture session.
Description
  A non streaming capture session is generally a frame by frame capture session.
  This event will only be triggered if ueFrame is in UsedEvents.
Parameters
  Sender   - The TJvAVICapture component triggering the event.
  videoHdr - A PJvVideoHdr structure containing informations about the frame.
See Also
  UsedEvents
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAVICapture.OnStatus
Summary
  The event triggered in case of a status change.
Description
  Use this event to follow the progress of a capture session.
  This event will only be triggered if ueStatus is in UsedEvents.
Parameters
