  str    - The string associated with that status change.
See Also
  UsedEvents
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAVICapture.OnVideoStream
Summary
  The event triggered when a frame is ready, in a streaming capture session.
Description
  This event is triggered just before the frame is written to disk. So if you make any
  changes to the frame in this event, they will be written to disk.
  This event will only be triggered if ueVideoStream is in UsedEvents.
Parameters
  Sender   - the TJvAVICapture component triggering the event.
  videoHdr - A PJvVideoHdr structure containing informations about the frame.
See Also
  UsedEvents
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAVICapture.OnWaveStream
Summary
  the event trigerred when an audio buffer is ready, during streaming capture.
Description
  This event is triggered just before the buffer is written do disk, leaving you the
  opportunity to modify it if needed.
  This event will only be triggered if ueAudioStream is in UsedEvents.
Parameters
  Sender  - the TJvAVICapture component triggering the event.
  waveHdr - the audio header describing the buffer.
See Also
  UsedEvents
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAVICapture.OnYield
Summary
