----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCaptureSettings.AbortLeftMouse
Summary
  Decides if the capture is aborted by a left click.
Description
  If set to true, any left click during the capture session will abort the capture.
See Also
  AbortRightMouse, KeyAbort, LimitEnabled, TimeLimit
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCaptureSettings.AbortRightMouse
Summary
  Decides if the capture is aborted by a right click.
Description
  If set to true, any right click during the capture session will abort the capture.
See Also
  AbortLeftMouse, KeyAbort, LimitEnabled, TimeLimit
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCaptureSettings.Apply
Summary
  Tries to apply the values set in the object to the TJvAVICapture object linked to this object.
