  Tries to apply the values set in the object to the TJvAVICapture object linked to this object.
Return value
  True if settings were applyed successfully, false otherwise.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCaptureSettings.AudioBufferSize
Summary
  The size in bytes of each audio buffer.
Description
  If left at the default value of 0, the size of each audio buffer will be the maximum of
  10 kbytes and 0.5 seconds of audio data.
See Also
